title: 14: Stiff Socks Take Singing Lessons
itunes:title: Stiff Socks Take Singing Lessons
description:
Stiff Socks learns to sing and discover they are definitely as good as Sam Smith, but not before discussing Trevor's birthright trip to Israel and why Soulja Boy is a huge inspiration.
